<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.4.1">
<l>aṉṟā yarkulak koṭiyō ṭaṇimā malarmaṅ kaiyoṭaṉ paḷavi yavuṇark</l>
<l>keṉṟā ṉumirak kamilā tavaṉuk kuṟaiyu miṭamā vatirum poḻilcūḻ</l>
<l>naṉṟā yapuṉal naṟaiyūrt tiruvā likuṭan taitaṭan tikaḻkō vaṉakar</l>
<l>niṉṟā ṉiruntāṉ kiṭantāṉ naṭantāṟ kiṭammā malaiyā vatunīr malaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For him who, having joined in love with the creeper[-like maid]</l>
<l rend="indent">of the herder clan and the lady of the great beautiful blossom,</l>
<l>Is always without pity for demons, the places where [he] dwells are namely</l>
<l>Well-watered Naṟaiyūr encircled by vast groves, Tiruvāli, Kuṭantai,</l>
<l rend="indent">and Kōvalūr, where ponds glimmer;</l>
<l>The place for him who stands, sits, lies, and strides</l>
<l rend="indent">is the great mountain, namely Nīrmalai.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
